00:29:23.723 --> 00:29:28.460 align:middle line:84%
The Tao is based on the unity of
the essential triad of heaven,

00:29:28.460 --> 00:29:31.080 align:middle line:90%
earth and humanity.

00:29:31.080 --> 00:29:33.540 align:middle line:84%
The ideal of the
Shaolin temple is

00:29:33.540 --> 00:29:38.640 align:middle line:84%
to enter the way by mastering
meditation and chi cultivation

00:29:38.640 --> 00:29:39.780 align:middle line:90%
as well as martial arts.

00:29:39.780 --> 00:29:53.230 align:middle line:90%


00:29:53.230 --> 00:29:57.810 align:middle line:84%
The creation of Tai Chi is based
on the thousand-year-old story

00:29:57.810 --> 00:30:01.800 align:middle line:84%
in which the founder
Chang San-Feng observed

00:30:01.800 --> 00:30:05.242 align:middle line:84%
an epic battle between
a crane and a snake.

00:30:05.242 --> 00:30:09.160 align:middle line:10%
He watched intently as the bird
fiercely attacked the snake

00:30:09.160 --> 00:30:11.010 align:middle line:10%
again and again.

00:30:11.010 --> 00:30:13.990 align:middle line:84%
With each attempt of the
bird to kill the snake,

00:30:13.990 --> 00:30:17.840 align:middle line:84%
the serpent's agility,
yielding and flowing movements

00:30:17.840 --> 00:30:20.270 align:middle line:90%
enabled it to survive.

00:30:20.270 --> 00:30:23.170 align:middle line:84%
The crane used its
speed and mobility

00:30:23.170 --> 00:30:25.370 align:middle line:84%
to avoid the snake's
counter attacks,

00:30:25.370 --> 00:30:26.960 align:middle line:90%
and also remained unharmed.

00:30:26.960 --> 00:30:33.010 align:middle line:90%


00:30:33.010 --> 00:30:35.440 align:middle line:84%
Chang San-Feng is
