00:31:39.330 --> 00:31:41.400 align:middle line:84%
is based on the
enlightened warrior

00:31:41.400 --> 00:31:45.120 align:middle line:84%
seeing his original face
and successfully cultivating

00:31:45.120 --> 00:31:47.880 align:middle line:90%
the spiritual embryo.

00:31:47.880 --> 00:31:50.990 align:middle line:84%
This has the potential of
transforming an individual

00:31:50.990 --> 00:31:53.240 align:middle line:84%
into an immortal,
