00:31:53.240 --> 00:31:57.780 align:middle line:90%


00:31:57.780 --> 00:32:00.370 align:middle line:84%
Many of the greatest
Chinese martial artists

00:32:00.370 --> 00:32:03.030 align:middle line:84%
actually achieved this
level of enlightenment,

00:32:03.030 --> 00:32:05.600 align:middle line:84%
and use their incredible
skills and power

00:32:05.600 --> 00:32:07.740 align:middle line:84%
to protect and
benefit their people.

00:32:07.740 --> 00:32:13.310 align:middle line:90%


00:32:13.310 --> 00:32:16.160 align:middle line:84%
A major aspect of
Chinese martial arts

00:32:16.160 --> 00:32:19.730 align:middle line:84%
is the transformation of
your three inner treasures--

00:32:19.730 --> 00:32:25.600 align:middle line:84%
jing, chi and chen--
within the body.

00:32:25.600 --> 00:32:30.100 align:middle line:84%
Often translated as reproductive
energy, vital bodily energy

00:32:30.100 --> 00:32:33.920 align:middle line:84%
and mind and spirit, they
are the most important aspect

00:32:33.920 --> 00:32:36.730 align:middle line:90%
of internal power development.

00:32:36.730 --> 00:32:38.860 align:middle line:84%
Their complete
refinement results

00:32:38.860 --> 00:32:43.070 align:middle line:84%
in the spiritual embryo and
immortality, a permanent state

00:32:43.070 --> 00:32:45.010 align:middle line:84%
of enlightened
consciousness that

00:32:45.010 --> 00:32:47.880 align:middle line:84%
is not limited by the
physical body and even

00:32:47.880 --> 00:32:49.300 align:middle line:90%
exists after death.

00:32:49.300 --> 00:32:53.230 align:middle line:90%


00:32:53.230 --> 00:32:55.890 align:middle line:84%
Complete mastery of
the sword has always

00:32:55.890 --> 00:32:57.365 align:middle line:84%
been a metaphor
for enlightenment.

00:32:57.365 --> 00:33:00.960 align:middle line:90%


00:33:00.960 --> 00:33:04.470 align:middle line:84%
The true sword represents
the enlightened mind.

00:33:04.470 --> 00:33:06.740 align:middle line:84%
And the enlightened
mind represents

00:33:06.740 --> 00:33:10.770 align:middle line:84%
discovering who you truly are
by seeing your original face.

00:33:10.770 --> 00:33:13.570 align:middle line:90%


00:33:13.570 --> 00:33:16.630 align:middle line:10%
Mastery of the sword
is based on the concept

00:33:16.630 --> 00:33:19.090 align:middle line:10%
that it is possible
