00:33:19.090 --> 00:33:22.890 align:middle line:10%
and realize compete inner
illumination by combining

00:33:22.890 --> 00:33:26.830 align:middle line:10%
meditation and qi cultivation
with a martial arts practice.

00:33:26.830 --> 00:33:50.790 align:middle line:90%


00:33:50.790 --> 00:33:52.690 align:middle line:84%
The legendary
alchemist and founder

00:33:52.690 --> 00:33:59.225 align:middle line:84%
