form, yet it has an essence.

00:34:05.900 --> 00:34:08.120 align:middle line:84%
It is hard to
understand and exists

00:34:08.120 --> 00:34:09.420 align:middle line:90%
like a shadow or an echo.

00:34:09.420 --> 00:34:13.960 align:middle line:90%


00:34:13.960 --> 00:34:16.659 align:middle line:90%
No one knows why this is.

00:34:16.659 --> 00:34:20.270 align:middle line:84%
Great spiritual warriors have
attained the Tao in the past,

00:34:20.270 --> 00:34:22.150 align:middle line:84%
