00:57:38.350 --> 00:57:46.320 align:middle line:90%


00:57:46.320 --> 00:57:48.995 align:middle line:84%
>>In China, many great
sages and alchemists

00:57:48.995 --> 00:57:53.440 align:middle line:84%
