00:58:02.350 --> 00:58:03.962 align:middle line:90%
dissolved into pure energy.

00:58:03.962 --> 00:58:11.658 align:middle line:90%


00:58:11.658 --> 00:58:16.340 align:middle line:84%
>>To the point where their
body and mind are engaged

00:58:16.340 --> 00:58:20.220 align:middle line:84%
in spiritual practice and
mystical illumination,

00:58:20.220 --> 00:58:23.810 align:middle line:84%
habitually, every
microsecond of the day,

00:58:23.810 --> 00:58:27.710 align:middle line:84%
