00:58:36.840 --> 00:58:39.520 align:middle line:84%
whether it's a
manifestation of stigmata,

00:58:39.520 --> 00:58:43.920 align:middle line:84%
manifestation of other
internal symbols on the bones

00:58:43.920 --> 00:58:45.715 align:middle line:84%
