disappearance, it all

00:58:55.280 --> 00:58:59.490 align:middle line:84%
depends on how that person has
engaged with spiritual practice

00:58:59.490 --> 00:59:04.410 align:middle line:84%
such that everything that
you are is in the process,

00:59:04.410 --> 00:59:05.640 align:middle line:90%
in the practice.

00:59:05.640 --> 00:59:07.685 align:middle line:84%
And I think that that's
what this is all about.

00:59:07.685 --> 00:59:09.500 align:middle line:84%
That spiritual
practice is really

00:59:09.500 --> 00:59:15.207 align:middle line:84%
about a total engagement of
every last atom in your body.

00:59:15.207 --> 00:59:19.410 align:middle line:90%


00:59:19.410 --> 00:59:23.150 align:middle line:84%
>>The goal of life is to
discover who we really.

00:59:23.150 --> 00:59:25.910 align:middle line:84%
At the highest level
of meditation and yoga

00:59:25.910 --> 00:59:28.440 align:middle line:84%
we see our original
face, and this

00:59:28.440 --> 00:59:31.610 align:middle line:84%
enables us to enter the
Tao and fully discover

00:59:31.610 --> 00:59:33.347 align:middle line:90%
who we have always really been.

00:59:33.347 --> 00:59:37.010 align:middle line:90%


00:59:37.010 --> 00:59:40.200 align:middle line:10%
>>What we're talking about,
in terms of spirituality,

00:59:40.200 --> 00:59:42.830 align:middle line:10%
in terms of the body, in
terms of enlightenment,

00:59:42.830 --> 00:59:45.560 align:middle line:10%
is we're making the
claim, along with all

00:59:45.560 --> 00:59:50.080 align:middle line:10%
the great historical traditions,
that there's something

00:59:50.080 --> 00:59:53.660 align:middle line:10%
more that we are already.

00:59:53.660 --> 00:59:57.770 align:middle line:10%
There's something more that
we can realize in our bodies

00:59:57.770 --> 01:00:03.160 align:middle line:10%
cannot be restricted merely to
a vast complex of desires which

01:00:03.160 --> 01:00:07.010 align:middle line:10%
will come to an end
with our last breath.

01:00:07.010 --> 01:00:11.730 align:middle line:10%
Khenpo Achos, this Tibetan monk,
out in his little Hermitage

01:00:11.730 --> 01:00:17.030 align:middle line:10%
in Eastern Tibet, breathing
his last with the words

01:00:17.030 --> 01:00:24.220 align:middle line:10%
om mani padme hum
and then dying.

01:00:24.220 --> 01:00:27.320 align:middle line:84%
And then his face turns into
the face of a little child,

01:00:27.320 --> 01:00:31.970 align:middle line:84%
pink and more alive than
the 81-year-old man who

01:00:31.970 --> 01:00:35.150 align:middle line:90%
said his final mantra.

01:00:35.150 --> 01:00:43.210 align:middle line:84%
>>Om mani padme hum, om mani
padme hum, om mani padme hum.

01:00:43.210 --> 01:01:00.380 align:middle line:90%


01:01:00.380 --> 01:01:02.710 align:middle line:84%
>>There is something
formed in chaos coming

01:01:02.710 --> 01:01:05.320 align:middle line:84%
before heaven and
earth, existing

01:01:05.320 --> 01:01:07.465 align:middle line:90%
in the silent and tranquil void.

01:01:07.465 --> 01:01:10.110 align:middle line:90%
It stands alone and unchanging.

01:01:10.110 --> 01:01:13.730 align:middle line:84%
It pervades everywhere
without becoming exhausted.

01:01:13.730 --> 01:01:16.820 align:middle line:84%
It is the mother of
heaven and earth.

01:01:16.820 --> 01:01:20.092 align:middle line:84%
I do not know its name,
and so call it Tao.

01:01:20.092 --> 01:01:27.170 align:middle line:90%


01:01:27.170 --> 01:01:29.910 align:middle line:84%
The future of modern
science is to discover

01:01:29.910 --> 01:01:31.210 align:middle line:90%
the mind of the Tao.

01:01:31.210 --> 01:01:34.840 align:middle line:90%


01:01:34.840 --> 01:01:37.640 align:middle line:84%
As science studies
meditation and the evolution

01:01:37.640 --> 01:01:40.580 align:middle line:84%
of consciousness,
the basic unification

01:01:40.580 --> 01:01:43.469 align:middle line:84%
of Eastern and Western
paradigms of the evolution

01:01:43.469 --> 01:01:44.760 align:middle line:90%
of consciousness is inevitable.

01:01:44.760 --> 01:01:49.710 align:middle line:90%


01:01:49.710 --> 01:01:51.660 align:middle line:84%
Modern science
will become focused

01:01:51.660 --> 01:01:53.890 align:middle line:84%
on enabling human
beings to achieve

01:01:53.890 --> 01:01:57.170 align:middle line:84%
their complete potential,
which is enlightenment.

01:01:57.170 --> 01:02:01.130 align:middle line:84%
Scientists will realize that the
completion stage of meditation

01:02:01.130 --> 01:02:04.460 align:middle line:84%
is the primordial vision
of the original face.

01:02:04.460 --> 01:02:06.750 align:middle line:84%
This represents
the ultimate level

01:02:06.750 --> 01:02:08.736 align:middle line:90%
of human mind/body evolution.

01:02:08.736 --> 01:02:14.840 align:middle line:90%


01:02:14.840 --> 01:02:19.920 align:middle line:84%
>>There are hints, there are
suggestions, that things go on

01:02:19.920 --> 01:02:23.260 align:middle line:84%
in the human body/mind complex
that have not been completely

01:02:23.260 --> 01:02:26.855 align:middle line:84%
explained by science, by
technology, by psychotherapy,

01:02:26.855 --> 01:02:29.740 align:middle line:90%
by quantum physics, or whatever.

01:02:29.740 --> 01:02:32.270 align:middle line:84%
So I think we're just being
invited to explore more deeply.

01:02:32.270 --> 01:02:34.686 align:middle line:84%
We may actually come up with
a new theory, a new paradigm.

01:02:34.686 --> 01:02:39.150 align:middle line:90%


01:02:39.150 --> 01:02:42.350 align:middle line:84%
>>Darwin's Theory of Evolution
does not include the fact

01:02:42.350 --> 01:02:44.880 align:middle line:84%
that the human reproductive
system is perfectly

01:02:44.880 --> 01:02:46.630 align:middle line:84%
designed to achieve
enlightenment,

01:02:46.630 --> 01:02:50.005 align:middle line:84%
and that this is actually
the purpose of the evolution

01:02:50.005 --> 01:02:50.713 align:middle line:90%
of consciousness.

01:02:50.713 --> 01:02:56.070 align:middle line:90%


01:02:56.070 --> 01:02:59.000 align:middle line:84%
Evolutionary psychology
is based on the idea

01:02:59.000 --> 01:03:01.910 align:middle line:84%
that all human behavior
is merely an attempt

01:03:01.910 --> 01:03:04.220 align:middle line:90%
to reproduce sexually.

01:03:04.220 --> 01:03:07.560 align:middle line:84%
The problem with this is that
it leaves out the basic fact

01:03:07.560 --> 01:03:10.230 align:middle line:84%
that the human reproductive
system is perfectly

01:03:10.230 --> 01:03:12.352 align:middle line:84%
designed to achieve
enlightenment

01:03:12.352 --> 01:03:15.970 align:middle line:84%
by unifying the pre-birth and
post-birth chi of the body.

01:03:15.970 --> 01:03:20.200 align:middle line:90%


01:03:20.200 --> 01:03:22.960 align:middle line:84%
This is the basis of the
Chinese medical system,

01:03:22.960 --> 01:03:24.880 align:middle line:84%
and represents the
future of science

01:03:24.880 --> 01:03:28.269 align:middle line:84%
in the 21st century as
the Philosopher's Stone is

01:03:28.269 --> 01:03:28.810 align:middle line:90%
rediscovered.

01:03:28.810 --> 01:03:34.450 align:middle line:90%


01:03:34.450 --> 01:03:38.180 align:middle line:84%
>>It shows that the
human body is a device

01:03:38.180 --> 01:03:41.010 align:middle line:84%
that the universe
itself has generated

01:03:41.010 --> 01:03:46.120 align:middle line:84%
enabling that enlightenment
to burst upon the scene.

01:03:46.120 --> 01:03:49.650 align:middle line:84%
In other words, your body,
with all its aches and pains,

01:03:49.650 --> 01:03:51.710 align:middle line:84%
and some people
tell us we weren't

01:03:51.710 --> 01:03:54.250 align:middle line:84%
meant to stand up on
two legs, and a lot

01:03:54.250 --> 01:03:56.170 align:middle line:84%
of problems that
have come into play

01:03:56.170 --> 01:03:58.600 align:middle line:84%
because of the shape of our
body and the way the organs

01:03:58.600 --> 01:04:00.010 align:middle line:90%
are set up.

01:04:00.010 --> 01:04:02.770 align:middle line:84%
But if you look at it from
a Buddhist point of view,

01:04:02.770 --> 01:04:07.340 align:middle line:84%
your body is set up so that the
energy goes from the perineum,

01:04:07.340 --> 01:04:10.500 align:middle line:84%
from the crotch, from
the base of the spine,

01:04:10.500 --> 01:04:14.400 align:middle line:84%
up through the subtle body
and the material body, both

01:04:14.400 --> 01:04:17.510 align:middle line:84%
in intimate union so that it
gets to the top of your head

01:04:17.510 --> 01:04:22.070 align:middle line:84%
and beyond so that you
can attain enlightenment.

01:04:22.070 --> 01:04:25.470 align:middle line:84%
If you were a
monkey or a dog, you

01:04:25.470 --> 01:04:27.474 align:middle line:84%
have some of those
same structures,

01:04:27.474 --> 01:04:29.140 align:middle line:84%
but they're not
positioned in such a way

01:04:29.140 --> 01:04:32.360 align:middle line:84%
to favor the attainment
of enlightenment.

01:04:32.360 --> 01:04:35.120 align:middle line:84%
So that you're sitting
in meditation in accord

01:04:35.120 --> 01:04:39.010 align:middle line:84%
with a certain set of
points that highlight,

01:04:39.010 --> 01:04:42.760 align:middle line:84%
accentuate and enhance
the inherent properties

01:04:42.760 --> 01:04:45.420 align:middle line:84%
of the human body to
attain enlightenment.

01:04:45.420 --> 01:04:46.880 align:middle line:84%
So this is a little
machine we've

01:04:46.880 --> 01:04:51.690 align:middle line:84%
been given for attaining that
high degree of consciousness.

01:04:51.690 --> 01:04:53.710 align:middle line:90%
This is magnificent stuff.

01:04:53.710 --> 01:04:55.450 align:middle line:84%
Because then you
suddenly realize,

01:04:55.450 --> 01:05:01.300 align:middle line:84%
oh, even if we did evolve from
so-called lower forms of life,

01:05:01.300 --> 01:05:05.370 align:middle line:84%
we are also in continuity
with those forms of life such

01:05:05.370 --> 01:05:13.500 align:middle line:84%
that what we attain is not just
private property, but is good,

01:05:13.500 --> 01:05:15.190 align:middle line:90%
cosmic benefit.

01:05:15.190 --> 01:05:17.742 align:middle line:84%
And then you get immediately
into the whole Bodhisattva vow,

01:05:17.742 --> 01:05:20.200 align:middle line:84%
the idea of doing this for the
sake of all sentient beings.

01:05:20.200 --> 01:05:40.550 align:middle line:90%


01:05:40.550 --> 01:05:43.050 align:middle line:84%
>>There is an ancient
story from China

01:05:43.050 --> 01:05:45.090 align:middle line:84%
in which a famous
zen master told

01:05:45.090 --> 01:05:48.920 align:middle line:84%
his student, if you see the
Buddha on the road, kill him.

01:05:48.920 --> 01:05:55.110 align:middle line:90%


01:05:55.110 --> 01:05:57.800 align:middle line:84%
What is meant by this
story is that your idea

01:05:57.800 --> 01:06:00.400 align:middle line:84%
of the Buddha as a sacred
figure to be worshipped

01:06:00.400 --> 01:06:05.080 align:middle line:84%
is incorrect, and is an illusion
that actually is blocking

01:06:05.080 --> 01:06:09.730 align:middle line:84%
your own perception of your
own awareness as enlightenment,

01:06:09.730 --> 01:06:13.840 align:middle line:84%
and your own realization
that you yourself have always

01:06:13.840 --> 01:06:15.150 align:middle line:90%
been a living Buddha.

01:06:15.150 --> 01:06:23.070 align:middle line:90%


01:06:23.070 --> 01:06:25.860 align:middle line:84%
The fully activated
starting point of the body

01:06:25.860 --> 01:06:27.030 align:middle line:90%
is your original face.

01:06:27.030 --> 01:06:30.510 align:middle line:90%


01:06:30.510 --> 01:06:33.210 align:middle line:84%
>>The Dalai Lama
says very clearly

01:06:33.210 --> 01:06:39.340 align:middle line:84%
how no self, Buddhist teaching
on no self and all of that,

01:06:39.340 --> 01:06:43.590 align:middle line:84%
is not about the destruction
of the personality.

01:06:43.590 --> 01:06:46.040 align:middle line:84%
It's a transformative
process that

01:06:46.040 --> 01:06:49.720 align:middle line:84%
has to do with who you
really are comes to the fore,

01:06:49.720 --> 01:06:53.200 align:middle line:90%
and what you are not disappears.

01:06:53.200 --> 01:06:56.650 align:middle line:84%
>>Buddhahood, immortality
or enlightenment actually

01:06:56.650 --> 01:06:59.690 align:middle line:84%
represent the true potential
of each human being

01:06:59.690 --> 01:07:02.080 align:middle line:90%
to fully awaken.

01:07:02.080 --> 01:07:04.260 align:middle line:84%
This is inevitably
going to be the goal

01:07:04.260 --> 01:07:06.210 align:middle line:84%
of the evolution
of consciousness

01:07:06.210 --> 01:07:07.202 align:middle line:90%
in the 21st century.

01:07:07.202 --> 01:07:11.750 align:middle line:90%


01:07:11.750 --> 01:07:14.680 align:middle line:10%
We are at the edge of time
when achieving enlightenment

01:07:14.680 --> 01:07:18.160 align:middle line:10%
will become a phenomenon
recognized by Western science

01:07:18.160 --> 01:07:20.800 align:middle line:10%
as both the completion
stage of meditation

01:07:20.800 --> 01:07:24.474 align:middle line:10%
and the achievement of matter,
energy and consciousness

01:07:24.474 --> 01:07:24.974 align:middle line:10%
unification.

01:07:24.974 --> 01:07:32.570 align:middle line:90%


01:07:32.570 --> 01:07:35.670 align:middle line:84%
When enough individuals
have activated the Kundalini

01:07:35.670 --> 01:07:39.230 align:middle line:84%
and seen their original
face within themselves,

01:07:39.230 --> 01:07:41.884 align:middle line:84%
the human race will be
completely transformed.

01:07:41.884 --> 01:08:01.970 align:middle line:90%


01:08:01.970 --> 01:08:04.330 align:middle line:10%
Already today,
millions of people

01:08:04.330 --> 01:08:08.270 align:middle line:10%
practice yoga, meditation,
Tai Chi and Qigong.

01:08:08.270 --> 01:08:15.600 align:middle line:90%


01:08:15.600 --> 01:08:18.060 align:middle line:84%
The complete evolution
of consciousness

01:08:18.060 --> 01:08:21.870 align:middle line:84%
is the result of these mind/body
arts when fully mastered.

01:08:21.870 --> 01:08:25.600 align:middle line:90%


01:08:25.600 --> 01:08:29.430 align:middle line:84%
The goal of our existence is
to reach our ultimate potential

01:08:29.430 --> 01:08:31.249 align:middle line:90%
as fully enlightened beings.

01:08:31.249 --> 01:08:37.670 align:middle line:90%


01:08:37.670 --> 01:08:41.970 align:middle line:84%
Bodhidharma said, our
original face is the mind.

01:08:41.970 --> 01:08:44.399 align:middle line:90%
The mind is our original face.

01:08:44.399 --> 01:08:47.325 align:middle line:84%
This mind is the same as
the mind of all Buddhas.

01:08:47.325 --> 01:08:51.200 align:middle line:90%


01:08:51.200 --> 01:08:55.600 align:middle line:84%
Buddhas of the past and future
merely transmit this mind.

01:08:55.600 --> 01:08:58.890 align:middle line:84%
Beyond your mind, there
is no Buddha anywhere,

01:08:58.890 --> 01:09:02.700 align:middle line:84%
but confused people don't
realize that their own mind is

01:09:02.700 --> 01:09:03.290 align:middle line:90%
the Buddha.

01:09:03.290 --> 01:09:06.250 align:middle line:90%


01:09:06.250 --> 01:09:10.080 align:middle line:84%
They keep searching for
truth outside of themselves.

01:09:10.080 --> 01:09:11.860 align:middle line:84%
Don't become lost
in such illusions.

01:09:11.860 --> 01:09:30.840 align:middle line:90%


01:09:30.840 --> 01:09:33.370 align:middle line:84%
Just realize that
there is no Buddha

01:09:33.370 --> 01:09:36.080 align:middle line:90%
outside of your own mind.

01:09:36.080 --> 01:09:38.710 align:middle line:84%
Wherever you are,
there is a Buddha.

01:09:38.710 --> 01:09:41.140 align:middle line:84%
Your mind has always
been a living Buddha.

01:09:41.140 --> 01:09:55.340 align:middle line:90%


01:09:55.340 --> 01:09:57.530 align:middle line:84%
So if you see a
Buddha on the road,

01:09:57.530 --> 01:10:00.420 align:middle line:84%
there is no need for
reverence-- just kill him,

01:10:00.420 --> 01:10:02.010 align:middle line:90%
because it is a false illusion.

01:10:02.010 --> 01:13:51.010 align:middle line:90%


01:13:51.010 --> 01:13:53.136 align:middle line:84%
If people will
cultivate the Tao,

01:13:53.136 --> 01:13:55.650 align:middle line:90%
their bodies will be strong.

01:13:55.650 --> 01:13:58.380 align:middle line:84%
By cultivating the
Tao for a long time,

01:13:58.380 --> 01:14:01.710 align:middle line:84%
one can transform
substance to spirit,

01:14:01.710 --> 01:14:06.450 align:middle line:84%
refining their body into subtle
energy and merge with the Tao.

01:14:06.450 --> 01:14:08.790 align:middle line:84%
Then their knowledge
is boundless,

01:14:08.790 --> 01:14:11.770 align:middle line:84%
and their physical
body is transcended.

01:14:11.770 --> 01:14:14.392 align:middle line:90%
This is the power of the Tao.

01:14:14.392 --> 01:14:18.640 align:middle line:90%


01:14:18.640 --> 01:14:22.200 align:middle line:84%
Speaking without speaking
and moving without moving

01:14:22.200 --> 01:14:26.780 align:middle line:84%
is called "the profound
and secret virtue."

01:14:26.780 --> 01:14:29.420 align:middle line:84%
You look at it and
it is not seen.

01:14:29.420 --> 01:14:32.080 align:middle line:90%
It is called "the formless."

01:14:32.080 --> 01:14:34.770 align:middle line:84%
You listen to it
and it is not heard,

01:14:34.770 --> 01:14:37.660 align:middle line:90%
it is called "the soundless."

01:14:37.660 --> 01:14:40.710 align:middle line:84%
You grasp it and
it cannot be held.

01:14:40.710 --> 01:14:43.840 align:middle line:10%
It is called "the intangible."

01:14:43.840 --> 01:14:46.650 align:middle line:84%
The ancient sages were
masters at penetrating

01:14:46.650 --> 01:14:51.030 align:middle line:90%
the subtle and profound Tao.

01:14:51.030 --> 01:14:54.260 align:middle line:84%
Can you hold the body
and spirit as one?

01:14:54.260 --> 01:14:57.460 align:middle line:84%
Concentrating your chi
and becoming pliant,

01:14:57.460 --> 01:15:00.610 align:middle line:84%
can you become like
a newborn baby?

01:15:00.610 --> 01:15:03.560 align:middle line:84%
Clearing your mind and
contemplating the profound,

01:15:03.560 --> 01:15:06.500 align:middle line:90%
can you remain unknown?

01:15:06.500 --> 01:15:10.270 align:middle line:84%
In understanding all things,
can you remain detached?

01:15:10.270 --> 01:15:16.270 align:middle line:90%


01:15:16.270 --> 01:15:19.600 align:middle line:84%
The highest enlightenment
is like water.

01:15:19.600 --> 01:15:25.212 align:middle line:84%
Water benefits all beings,
yet argues with no one.

01:15:25.212 --> 01:15:28.580 align:middle line:84%
It flows in unknown
places, and in this way

01:15:28.580 --> 01:15:30.870 align:middle line:90%
is close to the Tao.

01:15:30.870 --> 01:15:34.230 align:middle line:84%
Because the enlightened
do not go against nature,

01:15:34.230 --> 01:15:35.590 align:middle line:90%
they are one with the Tao.

01:15:35.590 --> 01:15:39.690 align:middle line:90%


01:15:39.690 --> 01:15:41.800 align:middle line:84%
The Tao that can
be put into words

01:15:41.800 --> 01:15:44.710 align:middle line:90%
is not the true and eternal Tao.

01:15:44.710 --> 01:15:50.200 align:middle line:84%
The Tao is an empty vessel-- it
is used, but never exhausted.

01:15:50.200 --> 01:15:52.065 align:middle line:84%
It is the fathomless
source of everything.

01:15:52.065 --> 01:15:59.995 align:middle line:90%


01:15:59.995 --> 01:16:02.560 align:middle line:84%
Under heaven, there is
nothing more yielding

01:16:02.560 --> 01:16:06.570 align:middle line:84%
and soft as water--
yet for attacking

01:16:06.570 --> 01:16:10.010 align:middle line:84%
what is hard and rigid,
there is nothing better.

01:16:10.010 --> 01:16:12.860 align:middle line:84%
In this way, the weak
can vanquish the strong

01:16:12.860 --> 01:16:15.192 align:middle line:84%
and the soft can
overcome the hard.

01:16:15.192 --> 01:16:20.280 align:middle line:90%


01:16:20.280 --> 01:16:22.280 align:middle line:90%
People follow the way of earth.

01:16:22.280 --> 01:16:25.110 align:middle line:90%
Earth follows the way of heaven.

01:16:25.110 --> 01:16:27.890 align:middle line:90%
Heaven follows the way of Tao.

01:16:27.890 --> 01:16:30.570 align:middle line:90%
Tao follows its own natural way.

01:16:30.570 --> 01:16:33.330 align:middle line:90%


01:16:33.330 --> 01:16:35.660 align:middle line:84%
There is something
formed in chaos coming

01:16:35.660 --> 01:16:38.260 align:middle line:84%
before heaven and
earth, existing

01:16:38.260 --> 01:16:40.820 align:middle line:90%
in the silent and tranquil void.

01:16:40.820 --> 01:16:43.120 align:middle line:90%
It stands alone and unchanging.

01:16:43.120 --> 01:16:46.680 align:middle line:84%
It pervades everywhere
without becoming exhausted.

01:16:46.680 --> 01:16:49.760 align:middle line:84%
It is the mother of
heaven and earth.

01:16:49.760 --> 01:16:53.010 align:middle line:84%
I do not know its name,
and so call it Tao.

01:16:53.010 --> 01:16:56.660 align:middle line:90%


01:16:56.660 --> 01:16:59.800 align:middle line:84%
To know others is
wisdom, but to master

01:16:59.800 --> 01:17:01.370 align:middle line:90%
one's self in enlightenment.

01:17:01.370 --> 01:17:04.810 align:middle line:90%


01:17:04.810 --> 01:17:07.790 align:middle line:84%
Those who conquer others
require great strength.

01:17:07.790 --> 01:17:12.320 align:middle line:84%
But to conquer one's
self requires true power.

01:17:12.320 --> 01:17:24.096 align:middle line:90%